        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-100 to-blue-50 text-sky-500 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-semibold shadow-sm">2</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Estudios médicos previos relacionados con su padecimiento actual</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-100 to-blue-50 text-sky-500 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 flex-shrink-0 text-sm font-semibold shadow-sm">3</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Lista de medicamentos que consume actualmente</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center">
